Mod 26

Cryptography can be easy, do you know what ROT13 is?
cvpbPGS{arkg_gvzr_V'yy_gel_2_ebhaqf_bs_ebg13_Ncualgvd}

The description hints at the string being encoded in ROT13.
Lets create a program Decode.sh to decode it.
Mark Decode.sh as executable using chmod +x Decode.sh
Eun Decode.sh using ./Decode,sh
Returns the flag:
"picoCTF{next_time_I'll_try_2_rounds_of_rot13_Aphnytiq}"

